data: The event Design Thinking Workshop had the main purpose of introducing design thinking principles to a collaborative team setting
The event Design Thinking Workshop covered empathy mapping as an insightful technique for understanding user perspectives
The event Design Thinking Workshop included brainstorming user pain points to inform solution ideation
The event Design Thinking Workshop emphasized rapid prototyping and timeboxing to maintain focus and accelerate idea refinement
The event Design Thinking Workshop resulted in the decision to choose Prototype A and schedule a follow-up session
The event Design Thinking Workshop generated action items to develop low-fidelity mockups and gather user feedback
